# Upload File

# Description

Upload your file through a previously created Chunk Uri.

# Untitled Section

# Configuration

* 
* Folder - The destination folder name. This field supports IResource type input. Use the Folder icon to browse your Citrix ShareFile folders.
* File resource - The file to upload. This field supports IResource type input. Use the Folder icon to browse your Citrix ShareFile folders.









* File ID - ID of the uploaded file. Automatically generated output variable.
* Upload file - Automatically generated output variable.
